      "UNITED\nAIR LINES\nA WORLD'S\nSTANDARD FOR\nSPEED PLUS LUXURY\n14½ hours from California to New York with\nonly 3 stops ... Chicago to New York non-stop\nin 3 hours 55 minutes . . . Los Angeles-San\nFrancisco 2 hours. These United Mainliners, built\nby Douglas, are the largest, most luxurious trans-\nports in the U. S. Backed by 110,000,000 miles\nof flying experience.\nPOST CARD\nPlease address\nand return to\nstewardess who\nwill stamp and\nmail card\nfor you.\n5"
